sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>HistoryScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ViewWorkoutHistory
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>WorkoutSession
  A->>B: open History tab
  B->>C: load()
  C->>E: listEndedSessions(userId, from = 1st of current month)
  note right of E: Free cap = current calendar<br/>month, enforced by the from filter
  E-->>C: this month's sessions
  C-->>B: grouped list + weekly analytics
  B-->>A: sessions, deltas, cap banner + upsell
  note over E: listEndedSessions via WorkoutGateway → workout_sessions (RLS: own rows)
